### =============================================================================
### ARQUIVO HTTP - TESTE DO MÓDULO DE WEIGHT RECORDS (HISTÓRICO DE PESO)
### Sistema: AUMIGOPET Engine
### Módulo: Weight Records
### =============================================================================

# Configuração de variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

# Variáveis de teste
@token = 
@weightRecordId = 
@petId = cmisz6ut10000kxjhzneszuon

### =============================================================================
### 1. AUTENTICAÇÃO
### =============================================================================

@token = {{loginUser.response.body.access_token}}
# @name loginUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "login": "user@aumigopet.com",
  "password": "User123@"
}

### =============================================================================
### 2. BUSCAR PETS (PARA OBTER petId)
### =============================================================================

### 2.0 Buscar pets do usuário logado
# @name getPets
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.0.1 Definir petId manualmente (use o ID retornado acima)
# Exemplo: @petId = clx1234567890abcdef
@petId = cmhawbehg0008ltkxfoynljnl

### =============================================================================
### 3. CRIAR REGISTROS DE PESO (CREATE)
### =============================================================================

### 3.1 Criar primeiro registro de peso
# @name createFirstWeight
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": 8.5,
  "date": "2025-01-25T00:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "NORMAL",
  "notes": "Peso inicial - adoção",
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### 3.2 Criar registro de peso abaixo do ideal
# @name createUnderweight
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": 6.2,
  "date": "2025-03-10T00:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "UNDERWEIGHT",
  "notes": "Pet recusando ração. Veterinário recomendou mudança de alimentação.",
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### 3.3 Criar registro de peso acima do ideal
# @name createOverweight
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": 10.8,
  "date": "2021-06-24T00:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "OVERWEIGHT",
  "notes": "Iniciando dieta e exercícios",
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### 3.4 Criar registro de peso atual
# @name createCurrentWeight
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": 9.3,
  "notes": "Peso estável após dieta",
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### =============================================================================
### 4. BUSCAR REGISTROS DE PESO (READ)
### =============================================================================

### 4.1 Buscar todos os registros
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.2 Buscar registro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records/{{weightRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.3 Buscar registros com paginação
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.4 Buscar registros por pet
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records?petId={{petId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.5 Buscar registros por status
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records?status=NORMAL
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.6 Buscar registros ordenados por data (mais recentes primeiro)
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records?petId={{petId}}&sortBy=date&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.7 Buscar registros em um período
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records?petId={{petId}}&startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =============================================================================
### 5. ATUALIZAR REGISTROS (UPDATE)
### =============================================================================

### 5.1 Atualizar notas do registro
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/weight-records/{{weightRecordId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "notes": "Atualizado: Pet está respondendo bem à dieta"
}

### 5.2 Corrigir peso registrado
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/weight-records/{{weightRecordId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": 9.5,
  "notes": "Correção de peso - balança estava descalibrada"
}

### 5.3 Atualizar status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/weight-records/{{weightRecordId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "NORMAL"
}

### =============================================================================
### 6. DELETAR REGISTROS (DELETE)
### =============================================================================

### 6.1 Deletar registro de peso
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/weight-records/{{weightRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =============================================================================
### 7. TESTES DE VALIDAÇÃO (ERROS ESPERADOS)
### =============================================================================

### 7.1 Criar registro sem autenticação (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "weight": 10.0,
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### 7.2 Criar registro com peso inválido (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": "dez quilos",
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### 7.3 Criar registro sem peso (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/weight-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "notes": "Sem peso",
  "petId": "{{petId}}"
}

### 7.4 Buscar registro inexistente (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/weight-records/id-inexistente
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### =============================================================================
### FIM DOS TESTES - WEIGHT RECORDS
### =============================================================================

